  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Greater Restoration</strong> (Level 5 Abjuration)</p><p>You imbue a creature you touch with positive energy to undo a debilitating effect. You can reduce the target's exhaustion level by one, or end one of the following effects on the target:</p><p>- One effect that charmed or petrified the target</p><p>- One curse, including the target's attunement to a cursed magic item</p><p>- Any reduction to one of the target's ability scores</p><p>- One effect reducing the target's hit point maximum</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (Diamond dust worth at least 100gp, which the spell consumes.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Touch | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Bard, Cleric, Druid</em></p>",
